<p>“let’s look at all the apps that live under our thumbs, and interrogate the choices they’re making, and then imagine what they would look like if we demanded that our tools don’t tie our hands.” - <a href="https://www.anildash.com/2019/12/10/link-in-bio-is-how-they-tried-to-kill-the-web/">Anil Dash</a> 💬</p>
<p>My take: <a href="https://writingslowly.com/2024/05/27/how-you-can.html">Don’t let your technology dictate your aesthetic experience</a>. We can make choices!</p>
